    <node ID="ID_348068464" TEXT="Lord God" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="179 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-2414 px" MIN_WIDTH="374" MAX_WIDTH="374">
      <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="74" BOLD="true"/>
      <node ID="ID_351582192" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="879 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="408 px" MIN_WIDTH="665" MAX_WIDTH="665">
        <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="59" BOLD="true"/>
        <edge COLOR="#30b082" WIDTH="6"/>
        <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 59pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">commanded the man</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 59pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic">Genesis 2:16</span></p>
        </body></html></richcontent>
        <node ID="ID_351608576" TEXT="“You are free to eat from any tree in the garden; but you must not eat from&quot;" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="97 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="332 px" MIN_WIDTH="791" MAX_WIDTH="791">
          <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="55" BOLD="true" ITALIC="true"/>
          <edge COLOR="#e24271" WIDTH="6"/>
          <arrowlink DESTINATION="ID_351887472" COLOR="#e24271" STARTARROW="NONE" ENDARROW="DEFAULT"/>
          <node ID="ID_351674920" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="746 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="321 px" MIN_WIDTH="445" MAX_WIDTH="445">
            <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="63" BOLD="true"/>
            <edge COLOR="#e24271" WIDTH="6"/>
            <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 63pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Because </span></p>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 63pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic">Genesis 2:17</span></p>
            </body></html></richcontent>
            <node ID="ID_351729144" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="610 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-362 px" MIN_WIDTH="941" MAX_WIDTH="941">
              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="33" BOLD="true"/>
              <edge COLOR="#e24271" WIDTH="6"/>
              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">in the day of your eating from it,</span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold"> dying you shall die</span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">of your eating</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff"> → אֲכָלְךָ (akhalka) — infinitive construct of אכל (akhal, "to eat, consume") with second person masculine singular suffix. Temporal, not conditional: </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff">"when you eat."</span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">dying</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff"> → מוֹת (mot) — infinitive absolute of מות (mut, "to die"). The intensifying construction — opens dying as a state entered, processual, not a single event.</span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">you shall die</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff"> → תָּמוּת (tamut) — second person masculine singular imperfect of מות. </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff">The finite verb completing the construction.</span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff">The infinitive absolute (mot) initiates a condition. The finite verb (tamut) completes it. </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff">Between them is the entire span of mortal life.</span></p>
              </body></html></richcontent>
            </node>
          </node>
        </node>
      </node>
    </node>
    <node ID="ID_351323192" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="10 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-285 px" MIN_WIDTH="417" MAX_WIDTH="417">
      <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
      <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Adam &amp; Eve</span></p>
        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Man and Woman</span></p>
        <p>&#160;</p>
        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Adam: Of the Earth / grounded</span></p>
        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Eve: Mother of the living / Life giver</span></p>
        <p>&#160;</p>
        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">After Adam and Eve eats the fruit of</span></p>
        <p>&#160;</p>
        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">The tree of knowing good and evil</span></p>
        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff"> </span></p>
        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Banished from paradise</span></p>
        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">To mortality</span></p>
        <p>&#160;</p>
        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Then they have children </span></p>
      </body></html></richcontent>
      <arrowlink DESTINATION="ID_351496832" COLOR="#000000" STARTARROW="NONE" ENDARROW="DEFAULT"/>
      <node ID="ID_351759288" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="645 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-34 px" MIN_WIDTH="470" MAX_WIDTH="470">
        <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
        <edge COLOR="#d07021" WIDTH="4"/>
        <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Cain</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"Given by God"</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">(to acquire)</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">The firstborn </span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Murdered Abel</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Envious / deceptive</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Represents maybe something</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">like our potential to mimic God</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Taking life and death into our own hands</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Like Cain did. Forgetting our place.</span></p>
        </body></html></richcontent>
        <node ID="ID_315230184" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="631 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="41 px" MIN_WIDTH="455" MAX_WIDTH="455">
          <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
          <edge COLOR="#e5a4a0" WIDTH="4"/>
          <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Enoch</span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">(To initiate / dedicate)</span></p>
            <p>&#160;</p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Civilization arises from</span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">the Cain impulse</span></p>
            <p>&#160;</p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"And he became a builder of a city, </span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">and he called the name of the city after </span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">the name of his son, Enoch."</span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Genesis 4:17</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff"> </span></p>
          </body></html></richcontent>
          <node ID="ID_351943272" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="579 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-25 px" MIN_WIDTH="418" MAX_WIDTH="418">
            <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
            <edge COLOR="#cc9d44" WIDTH="4"/>
            <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Irad</span></p>
              <p>&#160;</p>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff"> (Irad) — most likely from עִיר (ir), </span></p>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"city" or "watcher/guardian." </span></p>
              <p>&#160;</p>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">The עִירִין (irin) are the Watchers in </span></p>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Daniel 4 and the Enochic literature. </span></p>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">But in the civic reading: </span></p>
              <p>&#160;</p>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Enoch founds the city (Gen 4:17 — </span></p>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Cain names a city after him), </span></p>
              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">and Irad is what the city produces</span></p>
            </body></html></richcontent>
            <node ID="ID_352014856" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="601 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="305 px" MIN_WIDTH="600" MAX_WIDTH="600">
              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="24" BOLD="true"/>
              <edge COLOR="#d07021" WIDTH="4"/>
              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Mehuja'el (מְחוּיָאֵל)</span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff">P</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">ossible decompositions:</span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"Struck by Yah-God" — מְחוּ + יָ + אֵל — </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">two divine names compounded with violence</span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"Blotted out by God" — מחה + אֵל — </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">erasure, not impact </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">(same root as God erasing humanity in Gen 6:7)</span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"God reveals/declares" — חוה + אֵל — </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">same root as Chavvah/Eve</span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"God gives life" — חיה + אֵל — </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">root of mechayeh hametim, "reviver of the dead"</span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">The tension: the name is genuinely undecidable </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">between erasure, revelation, and life-giving. </span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">In the Cainite civilizational sequence, </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">this is the generation where </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">divine authority gets captured by human power  </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">and the ambiguity is the meaning. </span></p>
                <p>&#160;</p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">The sac</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic">red now means whatever </span></p>
                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic">the structure needs it to mean.</span></p>
              </body></html></richcontent>
              <node ID="ID_352075296" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="15 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="974 px" MIN_WIDTH="1035" MAX_WIDTH="1035">
                <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="26" BOLD="true"/>
                <edge COLOR="#cd3e24" WIDTH="4"/>
                <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Methushael (מְתוּשָׁאֵל)</span></p>
                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff">P</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">ossible decompositions:</span></p>
                  <p>&#160;</p>
                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"Man of God" — מְתוּ (man, cognate with Akkadian mutu) + אֵל</span></p>
                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"</span></p>
                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Man of Sheol" — מְתוּ + שְׁאוֹל, the divine and the grave compressed into one name</span></p>
                  <p>&#160;</p>
                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"Death of God" — מוּת (death) + אֵל, same consonants rearranged</span></p>
                  <p>&#160;</p>
                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"Demanded of God" — שָׁאַל (to ask/demand) + אֵל, compare Samuel/Shemu'el</span></p>
                </body></html></richcontent>
                <node ID="ID_352132520" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="1052 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="3 px" MIN_WIDTH="990" MAX_WIDTH="990">
                  <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="24" BOLD="true"/>
                  <edge COLOR="#c4752d" WIDTH="4"/>
                  <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                    <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Lamech (לֶמֶךְ)</span></p>
                    <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff">P</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">ossible decompositions:</span></p>
                    <p>&#160;</p>
                    <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"Br</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic">ought low" — </span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">from מוך (mukh), to be poor or diminished, with a ל- prefix</span></p>
                    <p>&#160;</p>
                    <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"Powerful one" — cognate with Arabic lamaka, to be strong</span></p>
                    <p>&#160;</p>
                    <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"To w</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic">hat purpose?" — fr</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">om למה (lamah), "why?</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic">", the</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic"> q</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">uestioning/despairing one</span></p>
                    <p>&#160;</p>
                    <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"Pr</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 24pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">iestly servant" — possibly from Sumerian/Akkadian lumakku, a cultic office</span></p>
                  </body></html></richcontent>
                  <arrowlink DESTINATION="ID_350675848" COLOR="#d07021" MIDDLE_LABEL="Father of" STARTARROW="NONE" ENDARROW="DEFAULT"/>
                  <arrowlink DESTINATION="ID_350770584" COLOR="#d07021" MIDDLE_LABEL="Father of" STARTARROW="NONE" ENDARROW="DEFAULT"/>
                </node>
              </node>
            </node>
          </node>
        </node>
      </node>
      <node ID="ID_351812520" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="720 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-84 px" MIN_WIDTH="333" MAX_WIDTH="333">
        <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
        <edge COLOR="#cccace" WIDTH="4"/>
        <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Abel</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">(A whif of air /</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Transient)</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">The after-thought</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Favored by God</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Murdered by Cain</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Represents something</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">like our potential to live</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">in perfect harmony with God</span></p>
        </body></html></richcontent>
      </node>
      <node ID="ID_351821272" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="1202 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="542 px" MIN_WIDTH="219" MAX_WIDTH="219">
        <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
        <edge COLOR="#cecf4d" WIDTH="4"/>
        <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Seth</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">(Put in place of /</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Plant firm)</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">The replacement </span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">for Abel, since we </span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">ruled Abel out by </span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">killing him</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Lived 912 years </span></p>
        </body></html></richcontent>
        <node ID="ID_352207208" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="289 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="592 px" MIN_WIDTH="797" MAX_WIDTH="797">
          <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="30" BOLD="true"/>
          <edge COLOR="#789dab" WIDTH="4"/>
          <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 30pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Enosh (אֱנוֹשׁ)</span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">P</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff">ossible decompositions:</span></p>
            <p>&#160;</p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff">"Mo</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">rtal man" — </span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff">enosh as frail, perishable man, </span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff">distinct from adam (earthling) and ish (individual)</span></p>
            <p>&#160;</p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff">"Sic</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">k/incurable" — f</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff">rom אנש, to be weak, desperate, terminal </span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff">(Jeremiah 17:9, the heart "desperately wicked")</span></p>
            <p>&#160;</p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff">"Companionable" — minority etymology, </span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff">cognate with Arabic ins (humankind) and uns (intimacy)</span></p>
            <p>&#160;</p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff">"Seth</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic"> also had a son, and he named him Enosh.</span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">At tha</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic">t time people began to call on the name of the Lord."</span></p>
            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic">Gene</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">sis 4:26</span></p>
          </body></html></richcontent>
