                    <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">God took him</span></p>
                  </body></html></richcontent>
                  <node ID="ID_352378016" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="34 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="504 px" MIN_WIDTH="338" MAX_WIDTH="338">
                    <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                    <edge COLOR="#4e615c" WIDTH="4"/>
                    <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                      <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Methuselah</span></p>
                      <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">(his death sends a projectile)</span></p>
                      <p>&#160;</p>
                      <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">When this one dies, </span></p>
                      <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">something is launched. </span></p>
                      <p>&#160;</p>
                      <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Lived 969 years</span></p>
                      <p>&#160;</p>
                      <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">He dies the year of the flood </span></p>
                    </body></html></richcontent>
                    <node ID="ID_352427232" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="70 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="462 px" MIN_WIDTH="485" MAX_WIDTH="485">
                      <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                      <edge COLOR="#cecf4d" WIDTH="4"/>
                      <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Lamech</span></p>
                        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">see etymology above</span></p>
                        <p>&#160;</p>
                        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">He names his son Noah and says: </span></p>
                        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"This one will comfort us from our work </span></p>
                        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">and the toil of our hands, from the ground </span></p>
                        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">which the LORD has cursed."</span></p>
                        <p>&#160;</p>
                        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Lived 777 years </span></p>
                        <p>&#160;</p>
                        <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">He dies 5 years before the flood</span></p>
                      </body></html></richcontent>
                      <node ID="ID_352464544" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="30 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="588 px" MIN_WIDTH="590" MAX_WIDTH="590">
                        <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="40" BOLD="true"/>
                        <edge COLOR="#789dab" WIDTH="4"/>
                        <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 40pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Noah</span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 40pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">"Rest" or </span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 40pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">"Settle"</span></p>
                          <p>&#160;</p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 23pt; color: #ffffff">Builds the Ark and</span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 23pt; color: #ffffff">survives the cataclysm</span></p>
                          <p>&#160;</p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 23pt; color: #ffffff">Bridge between </span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 23pt; color: #ffffff">the old world and</span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 23pt; color: #ffffff">the new</span></p>
                          <p>&#160;</p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff">The people who survived </span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff">the Cataclysm split into three </span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff">cultures</span></p>
                          <p>&#160;</p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 23pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">The Bible tells the story from a Shem perspective</span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 23pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">So Japheth and Ham are secondary</span></p>
                          <p>&#160;</p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff">Lived 950 years</span></p>
                          <p>&#160;</p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 20pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">This is the first splitting / division</span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 20pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">When one becomes many</span></p>
                          <p>&#160;</p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 20pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">The symbolism of Jesus (God's son)</span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 20pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"dying on the cross" suddenly seems apt.</span></p>
                          <p>&#160;</p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 20pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"The Crux of the matter"</span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 20pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">God is the Word</span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 20pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">He sends his son, the Word in flesh</span></p>
                          <p>&#160;</p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 20pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">It is perfect, but upon contact with humanity</span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 20pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">it is killed on the cross. The cross is a universal </span></p>
                          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 20pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">symbol for division.</span></p>
                        </body></html></richcontent>
                        <node ID="ID_352560936" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="828 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="238 px" MIN_WIDTH="486" MAX_WIDTH="486">
                          <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="38" BOLD="true"/>
                          <edge COLOR="#a3dd8a" WIDTH="4"/>
                          <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 38pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Shem</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 38pt; color: #ffffff">"Name"</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 38pt; color: #ffffff">(Name / </span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 38pt; color: #ffffff">essence /</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 38pt; color: #ffffff">substance</span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Covers up father's </span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">nakedness </span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"Blessed be the LORD, </span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">the God of Shem."</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Genesis 9:26</span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">They chose to cover up but preserve </span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">old world knowledge. The Abrahamic line.</span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Shem also intermixed culture and </span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">most likely religion with Japheth and Ham</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">on various occasions</span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Lived 600 years</span></p>
                          </body></html></richcontent>
