                                              <p>&#160;</p>
                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 37pt; color: #ffffff">Becomes Abraham </span></p>
                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 37pt; color: #ffffff">the added "ha" represents</span></p>
                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 37pt; color: #ffffff">a piece of God added to</span></p>
                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 37pt; color: #ffffff">his name / essence after</span></p>
                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 37pt; color: #ffffff">their covenant was made </span></p>
                                              <p>&#160;</p>
                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 37pt; color: #ffffff">Lives 175 years</span></p>
                                            </body></html></richcontent>
