                                                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"He laughs"</span></p>
                                                  <p>&#160;</p>
                                                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Abram and Sarah laughs when God </span></p>
                                                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">tells them to have another child, due to </span></p>
                                                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">their old age. God tells them to name him</span></p>
                                                  <p>&#160;</p>
                                                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Yitzhak — "he laughs."</span></p>
                                                  <p>&#160;</p>
                                                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"God has made laughter for me. </span></p>
                                                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Everyone who hears will laugh with me."</span></p>
                                                </body></html></richcontent>
