                                                                  <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 37pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"My God is help"</span></p>
                                                                </body></html></richcontent>
                                                              </node>
                                                            </node>
                                                          </node>
                                                          <node ID="ID_228698576" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="466 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-899 px" MIN_WIDTH="578" MAX_WIDTH="578">
                                                            <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="33" BOLD="true"/>
                                                            <edge COLOR="#9a7c93" WIDTH="4"/>
                                                            <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Aaron</span></p>
                                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 33pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">The High Priest</span></p>
                                                              <p>&#160;</p>
                                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">After God consumes his first</span></p>
                                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">and second son, Moses tells him</span></p>
                                                              <p>&#160;</p>
                                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"This is what the LORD meant when He said,</span></p>
                                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic"> 'through those near to me I will be sanctified, </span></p>
                                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">and before all the people I will be glorified.'"</span></p>
                                                              <p>&#160;</p>
                                                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 25pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Aaron's response was silence </span></p>
                                                            </body></html></richcontent>
                                                            <node ID="ID_97184176" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="97 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-451 px" MIN_WIDTH="300" MAX_WIDTH="300">
                                                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                                                              <edge COLOR="#be4781" WIDTH="4"/>
                                                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Nadab</span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"generous" or </span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"willing"</span></p>
                                                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Sees God and lives</span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">But then disrespects God</span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">somehow and is </span></p>
                                                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">consumed by God</span></p>
                                                              </body></html></richcontent>
                                                            </node>
                                                            <node ID="ID_93127584" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="398 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-115 px" MIN_WIDTH="298" MAX_WIDTH="298">
                                                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                                                              <edge COLOR="#be4781" WIDTH="4"/>
                                                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Abihu</span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"He is my father"</span></p>
                                                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Same story as Nadab</span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Also consumed by God</span></p>
                                                              </body></html></richcontent>
                                                            </node>
                                                            <node ID="ID_227617776" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="480 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="202 px" MIN_WIDTH="417" MAX_WIDTH="417">
                                                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                                                              <edge COLOR="#be4781" WIDTH="4"/>
                                                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Eleazar</span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"God has helped"</span></p>
                                                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Becomes high priest after Aaron dies</span></p>
                                                              </body></html></richcontent>
                                                            </node>
                                                            <node ID="ID_343076696" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="456 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="475 px" MIN_WIDTH="354" MAX_WIDTH="354">
                                                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                                                              <edge COLOR="#be4781" WIDTH="4"/>
                                                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Ithamar</span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Possibly "island/land of palms"</span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Etymology uncertain </span></p>
                                                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Oversees the Gershonites and</span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff"> Merarites in the tabernacle</span></p>
                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff"> construction.</span></p>
                                                              </body></html></richcontent>
                                                            </node>
                                                          </node>
