                                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff"> The word also carries erotic connotations </span></p>
                                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff">Song of Songs uses דוֹדִי (dodi, "my beloved") throughout.</span></p>
                                                                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff"> The king is the beloved one.</span></p>
