                        <node ID="ID_318522336" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="867 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="107 px" MIN_WIDTH="589" MAX_WIDTH="589">
                          <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="38" BOLD="true"/>
                          <edge COLOR="#a3dd8a" WIDTH="4"/>
                          <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 38pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Japheth</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 38pt; color: #ffffff">"The Expanded One"</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 38pt; color: #ffffff">"The One Who Spreads Wide"</span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Covers up father's nakedness</span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"May God enlarge Japheth, </span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">and let him dwell in the tents of Shem. </span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">and let Canaan be his servant."</span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 17pt; color: #ffffff">It seems clear that Shem and Japheth part</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 17pt; color: #ffffff">on good terms, "Let them dwell in our tents".</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 17pt; color: #ffffff">The Canaan-servant comment seems important:</span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff">They understand that Ham will be strong initially,</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff">but that they can't sustain it. </span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff">So it is Canaan (and his sons), not</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff">Ham that will one day have to serve Japheth.</span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 15pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">This culture refuses to exploit old world</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 15pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">knowledge, and branches off into various </span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 15pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">cultures with their own mythologies</span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 15pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">For more insight into Japheth cultures,</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 15pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">look into the older world religions</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 15pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">that did not branch out of Shem. </span></p>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 15pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">The Hindu religions, Greek/Norse mythology,</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 15pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">and many others. Likely intermixed with</span></p>
                            <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 15pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Shem and Ham cultures on many occasions</span></p>
                          </body></html></richcontent>
                          <node ID="ID_349568216" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="1315 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-426 px" MIN_WIDTH="547" MAX_WIDTH="547">
                            <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                            <edge COLOR="#35e1c8" WIDTH="4"/>
                            <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Gomer</span></p>
                              <p>&#160;</p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">traditionally identified with the Cimmerians </span></p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">(Akkadian Gimirrāya), an Indo-European people </span></p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">who appeared north of the Black Sea and later </span></p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">swept into Anatolia</span></p>
                            </body></html></richcontent>
                            <node ID="ID_349996880" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="854 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-236 px" MIN_WIDTH="558" MAX_WIDTH="558">
                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                              <edge COLOR="#8f6a3d" WIDTH="4"/>
                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Ashkenaz</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Scythians (Pontic steppe)</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Jeremiah 51:27 calls up "the kingdoms of Ararat, </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Minni, and Ashkenaz" against Babylon</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Later appropriated, this is not the same as the</span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Ashkenazi Jews</span></p>
                              </body></html></richcontent>
                            </node>
                            <node ID="ID_350059312" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="36 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-330 px" MIN_WIDTH="170" MAX_WIDTH="170">
                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                              <edge COLOR="#8f6a3d" WIDTH="4"/>
                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Riphath</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">No one knows</span></p>
                              </body></html></richcontent>
                            </node>
                            <node ID="ID_349827032" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="1034 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="177 px" MIN_WIDTH="638" MAX_WIDTH="638">
                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                              <edge COLOR="#8f6a3d" WIDTH="4"/>
                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Togarmah</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Tegarama in Hittite records, Til-garimmu in </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Assyrian, a city and region in eastern Anatolia </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">(probably near modern Gürün in Turkey, </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">in the upper Euphrates area). </span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">It was a significant Late Bronze Age center, </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">destroyed by Sennacherib in 695 BCE. </span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Ezekiel 27:14 says "Beth-togarmah exchanged horses, </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">war horses, and mules for your wares" — </span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Eastern Anatolia was indeed prime horse-breeding </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">country, and this fits the Cappadocian/Armenian </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">highland economy precisely.</span></p>
                              </body></html></richcontent>
                            </node>
                          </node>
                          <node ID="ID_349683632" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="181 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-318 px" MIN_WIDTH="229" MAX_WIDTH="229">
                            <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="26" BOLD="true"/>
                            <edge COLOR="#35e1c8" WIDTH="4"/>
                            <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Magog</span></p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff">"the far north"</span></p>
                              <p>&#160;</p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 26pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Gog from Magog</span></p>
                            </body></html></richcontent>
                          </node>
                          <node ID="ID_349741624" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="927 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="370 px" MIN_WIDTH="780" MAX_WIDTH="780">
                            <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                            <edge COLOR="#35e1c8" WIDTH="4"/>
                            <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Madai</span></p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Iranian people of the Zagros, capital Ecbatana, later absorbed into the Achaemenid empire</span></p>
                            </body></html></richcontent>
                          </node>
                          <node ID="ID_349500944" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="722 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="779 px" MIN_WIDTH="501" MAX_WIDTH="501">
                            <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                            <edge COLOR="#35e1c8" WIDTH="4"/>
                            <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Javan</span></p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">the Ionians (Greek Iáwones, Hebrew Yāwān)</span></p>
                            </body></html></richcontent>
                            <node ID="ID_350179568" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="753 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-445 px" MIN_WIDTH="370" MAX_WIDTH="370">
                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                              <edge COLOR="#8f6a3d" WIDTH="4"/>
                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Elishah</span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">almost certainly Alashiya, </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">the Bronze Age name for Cyprus</span></p>
                              </body></html></richcontent>
                            </node>
                            <node ID="ID_350241560" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="1623 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-287 px" MIN_WIDTH="773" MAX_WIDTH="773">
                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                              <edge COLOR="#8f6a3d" WIDTH="4"/>
                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Tarshish</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">the famously contested one. Candidates:</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Tartessos in southwestern Spain (Guadalquivir region) — </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">a </span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">wealthy Phoenician trading partner known for silver, tin, lead. </span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">This is the dominant scholarly identification and fits </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Ezekiel 27:12 ("Tarshish did business with you because of </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">your great wealth of every kind; silver, iron, tin, </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">and lead they exchanged for your wares").</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">T</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">arsus in Cilicia (southern Anatolia) — phonetically tempting, geographically much closer.</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Sardinia — there's a 9th c. BCE Phoenician inscription from Nora, </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Sardinia, that contains the word tršš, which some read as Tarshish.</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">  A generic "far west" — </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">by the time of Jonah, </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"ships of Tarshish" had </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">become an idiom for large oceangoing vessels, </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">  and "fleeing to Tarshish" meant fleeing to the end </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">of the known world </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">(which is the whole point of Jonah </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">going there to escape Nineveh —</span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">opposite direction, edge of the map).</span></p>
                              </body></html></richcontent>
                            </node>
                            <node ID="ID_350311528" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="1004 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="620 px" MIN_WIDTH="575" MAX_WIDTH="575">
                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                              <edge COLOR="#8f6a3d" WIDTH="4"/>
                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Kittim</span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Kition, the major Phoenician city-state </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">on Cyprus (modern Larnaca). Originally just </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"people of Kition," then broadened to mean </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Cypriots generally, then broadened again to </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">mean "westerners across the sea." </span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">By the Hellenistic period it covers </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Macedonians and Greeks (1 Maccabees calls </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Alexander a king "from the land of Kittim"), </span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">and by the Roman period the Qumran sectarians </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">use Kittim as their code-word for the Romans — </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">the War Scroll's eschatological enemy is </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"the Kittim of Asshur" and "the Kittim in Egypt." </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">So Kittim has this fascinating semantic drift: </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">Cypriot city → Cyprus → Greeks → Romans → </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">eschatological western oppressor. </span></p>
                                <p>&#160;</p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">It tracks the Levantine experience of </span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">"who is currently invading us from the sea."</span></p>
                              </body></html></richcontent>
                            </node>
                            <node ID="ID_350386616" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="240 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="1247 px" MIN_WIDTH="188" MAX_WIDTH="188">
                              <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                              <edge COLOR="#8f6a3d" WIDTH="4"/>
                              <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Dodanim</span></p>
                                <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">May be Rhodes</span></p>
                              </body></html></richcontent>
                            </node>
                          </node>
                          <node ID="ID_349905504" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="left" HGAP_QUANTITY="515 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="1474 px" MIN_WIDTH="725" MAX_WIDTH="725">
                            <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                            <edge COLOR="#35e1c8" WIDTH="4"/>
                            <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Tubal &amp; Meshech</span></p>
                              <p>&#160;</p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">The Tabal and Mushki of Assyrian records, Anatolian kingdoms in eastern/central Asia Minor, post-Hittite. Herodotus' Tibarenoi and Moschoi.</span></p>
                            </body></html></richcontent>
                          </node>
                          <node ID="ID_349961056" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#141414" COLOR="#ffffff" POSITION="right" HGAP_QUANTITY="275 px" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="1471 px" MIN_WIDTH="459" MAX_WIDTH="459">
                            <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
                            <edge COLOR="#35e1c8" WIDTH="4"/>
                            <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Tiras</span></p>
                              <p>&#160;</p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">most likely the Tyrsenoi/Tyrrhenians, </span></p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">i.e., the sea peoples that Greek tradition </span></p>
                              <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic">links to the Etruscans' origin. </span></p>
                            </body></html></richcontent>
                          </node>
