        <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
        <edge COLOR="#e24271" WIDTH="4"/>
        <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Adah (עָדָה)</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Possible decompositions:</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"Ornament/adornment" — </span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">from עדה (  adah), to adorn, to </span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">deck oneself</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">"</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Witness/testimony" — </span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">from עֵד (  ed), witness, with a feminine suffix</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"To advance/pass by" — </span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">from עדה (adah), to pass, to move forward</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"Pleasure/delight" — </span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">from עדן (eden), same consonantal field as Eden itself</span></p>
        </body></html></richcontent>
