        <font NAME="LiberationSans" SIZE="22" BOLD="true"/>
        <edge COLOR="#858088" WIDTH="4"/>
        <richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html><head/><body>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">Zillah (צִלָּה)</span></p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">Possible decompositions:</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"Shadow" — from צֵל (tzel), shadow, shade</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"Ringing/clanging" — from צלל (tzalal), to ring, to vibrate, to resound</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"Protection" — צֵל as shelter, "in t</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">he shadow of," as i</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">n Psalm 91:1</span></p>
          <p>&#160;</p>
          <p><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">"Dark one" — shadow as absenc</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">e of light, the h</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff">i</span><span style="font-family: LiberationSans; font-size: 22pt; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold">dden</span></p>
        </body></html></richcontent>
